									<strong>理论课教学内容 </strong>:</div>
							</TD>
							<TD width="116" height="32" ALT=""></TD>
						</TR>
						<TR>
							<TD colspan="2" align="center"><div class="text" style="PADDING-RIGHT: 25px; PADDING-LEFT: 25px; COLOR: #000000; PADDING-TOP: 1px">
							  <table width="200" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="10">
                                <tr>
                                  <td><img src="images/jiaocai.jpg" width="100" height="145"></td>
                                  <td><img src="images/dbc.jpg" width="166" height="131"></td>
